    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Seats for a rider, made of various materials including wood, leather or textiles, which may be secured to the back of a camel by means of a girth passing under the body.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
